  <answer><![CDATA[<p>Santa Breaks are not recommended for very small infants under 3 years of age. Toddlers 3 years+  generally love the excitement and magic of it all including the Santa’s Workshop.</p>
<p>Although children under 4 years old are not able to join any snowmobile safaris, it's possible for them to join the husky &amp; reindeer safari excursion, under the care and supervision of an adult.</p>]]></answer>
